"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#uniqueDiffWithinAt_iff","kind":"theorem","line":142,"name":"uniqueDiffWithinAt_iff","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.lean#L142-L142"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">structure</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#UniqueDiffWithinAt\"><span class=\"name\">UniqueDiffWithinAt</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">R</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">E</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> v}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Ring/Defs.html#Semiring\">Semiring</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#AddCommGroup\">AddCommGroup</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Module/Defs.html#Module\">Module</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Basic.html#TopologicalSpace\">TopologicalSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set\">Set</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">E</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A property ensuring that the tangent cone to `s` at `x` spans a dense subset of the whole space.\nThe main role of this property is to ensure that the differential within `s` at `x` is unique,\nhence this name. The uniqueness it asserts is proved in `UniqueDiffWithinAt.eq` in\n`Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/FDeriv/Basic.lean`.\nTo avoid pathologies in dimension 0, we also require that `x` belongs to the closure of `s` (which\nis automatic when `E` is not `0`-dimensional). ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#UniqueDiffWithinAt","kind":"structure","line":136,"name":"UniqueDiffWithinAt","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.lean#L136-L145"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#posTangentConeAt\"><span class=\"name\">posTangentConeAt</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">E</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> v}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#AddCommGroup\">AddCommGroup</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Module/Defs.html#Module\">Module</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Real/Basic.html#Real\">ℝ</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Basic.html#TopologicalSpace\">TopologicalSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set\">Set</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">E</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set\">Set</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"\"Positive\" tangent cone to `s` at `x`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#posTangentConeAt","kind":"def","line":129,"name":"posTangentConeAt","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.lean#L129-L132"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#exists_fun_of_mem_tangentConeAt\"><span class=\"name\">exists_fun_of_mem_tangentConeAt</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">R</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">E</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> v}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#AddCommGroup\">AddCommGroup</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#SMul\">SMul</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Basic.html#TopologicalSpace\">TopologicalSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set\">Set</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x </span><span class=\"fn\">y</span> : <span class=\"fn\">E</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">h</span> : <span class=\"fn\">y</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#tangentConeAt\">tangentConeAt</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">s</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">∃ (<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> (max u v)) (<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter\">Filter</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>) (_ : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">l</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.NeBot\">NeBot</a></span>) (<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">R</span></span>) (<span class=\"fn\">d</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>),\n  <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.Tendsto\">Filter.Tendsto</a> <span class=\"fn\">d</span> <span class=\"fn\">l</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Filter.html#nhds\">nhds</a> <span class=\"fn\">0</span>)</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.Eventually\">∀ᶠ</a> (<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>) <a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.Eventually\">in</a> <span class=\"fn\">l</span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.Eventually\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\">x</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HAdd.hAdd\">+</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">d</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\">s</span>)</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.Tendsto\">Filter.Tendsto</a> <span class=\"fn\">(fun (<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">c</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSMul.hSMul\">•</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">d</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">l</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Filter.html#nhds\">nhds</a> <span class=\"fn\">y</span>)</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"If `y` belongs to the tangent cone of `s` at `x`, then there exist\n\n- an index type `α` and a nontrivial filter `l` on `α`;\n- a family of scalars `c n`, `n : α`, and a family of vectors `d n`, `n : α` such that\n- `d n → 0` along `l`;\n- `x + d n ∈ s` eventually along `l`;\n- `c n • d n → y` along `l`.\n\nIn fact, one can take `α = R × E`, `c = Prod.fst`, and `d = Prod.snd`, but this is not important,\nso the lemma statement hides these details.\n\nThis lemma provides a convenient way to unfold the definition of `tangentConeAt`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#exists_fun_of_mem_tangentConeAt","kind":"theorem","line":100,"name":"exists_fun_of_mem_tangentConeAt","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.lean#L100-L125"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#mem_tangentConeAt_of_seq\"><span class=\"name\">mem_tangentConeAt_of_seq</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">R</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">E</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> v}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#AddCommGroup\">AddCommGroup</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#SMul\">SMul</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Basic.html#TopologicalSpace\">TopologicalSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set\">Set</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x </span><span class=\"fn\">y</span> : <span class=\"fn\">E</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter\">Filter</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">l</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.NeBot\">NeBot</a></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">R</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">d</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hd₀</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.Tendsto\">Filter.Tendsto</a> <span class=\"fn\">d</span> <span class=\"fn\">l</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Filter.html#nhds\">nhds</a> <span class=\"fn\">0</span>)</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hds</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.Eventually\">∀ᶠ</a> (<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>) <a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.Eventually\">in</a> <span class=\"fn\">l</span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.Eventually\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\">x</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HAdd.hAdd\">+</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">d</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\">s</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hcd</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.Tendsto\">Filter.Tendsto</a> <span class=\"fn\">(fun (<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">c</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSMul.hSMul\">•</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">d</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">l</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Filter.html#nhds\">nhds</a> <span class=\"fn\">y</span>)</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">y</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#tangentConeAt\">tangentConeAt</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">s</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A special case of `mem_tangentConeAt_of_frequently`, which avoids `Filter.Frequently`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#mem_tangentConeAt_of_seq","kind":"theorem","line":94,"name":"mem_tangentConeAt_of_seq","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.lean#L94-L98"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#mem_tangentConeAt_of_frequently\"><span class=\"name\">mem_tangentConeAt_of_frequently</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">R</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">E</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> v}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#AddCommGroup\">AddCommGroup</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#SMul\">SMul</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Basic.html#TopologicalSpace\">TopologicalSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set\">Set</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x </span><span class=\"fn\">y</span> : <span class=\"fn\">E</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter\">Filter</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">R</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">d</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hd₀</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.Tendsto\">Filter.Tendsto</a> <span class=\"fn\">d</span> <span class=\"fn\">l</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Filter.html#nhds\">nhds</a> <span class=\"fn\">0</span>)</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hds</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.Frequently\">∃ᶠ</a> (<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>) <a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.Frequently\">in</a> <span class=\"fn\">l</span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.Frequently\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\">x</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HAdd.hAdd\">+</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">d</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\">s</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hcd</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.Tendsto\">Filter.Tendsto</a> <span class=\"fn\">(fun (<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">c</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSMul.hSMul\">•</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">d</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">l</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Filter.html#nhds\">nhds</a> <span class=\"fn\">y</span>)</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">y</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#tangentConeAt\">tangentConeAt</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">s</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Let `c n` be a family of scalars, `d n` be a family of vectors, and `l` be a filter such that\n\n- `d n → 0` along `l`;\n- `x + d n ∈ s` frequently along `l`;\n- `c n • d n → y` along `l`.\n\nThen `y` belongs to the tangent cone of `s` at `x`.\nSee also\n\n- `mem_tangentConeAt_of_seq` for a version assuming that `x + d n ∈ s` eventually along `l`.\n- `exists_fun_of_mem_tangentConeAt` for the other implication.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#mem_tangentConeAt_of_frequently","kind":"theorem","line":70,"name":"mem_tangentConeAt_of_frequently","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.lean#L70-L92"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#tangentConeAt_def\"><span class=\"name\">tangentConeAt_def</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">R</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">E</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#AddCommGroup\">AddCommGroup</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#SMul\">SMul</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Basic.html#TopologicalSpace\">TopologicalSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set\">Set</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">E</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#tangentConeAt\">tangentConeAt</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">s</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#setOf\">{</a><span class=\"fn\">y</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#setOf\">:</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#setOf\">|</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Filter.html#ClusterPt\">ClusterPt</a> <span class=\"fn\">y</span> (<a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Notation.html#Top.top\">⊤</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSMul.hSMul\">•</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Filter.html#nhdsWithin\">nhdsWithin</a> <span class=\"fn\">0</span> (<span class=\"fn\">(fun (<span class=\"fn\">x_1</span> : <span class=\"fn\">E</span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\">x</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HAdd.hAdd\">+</a> <span class=\"fn\">x_1</span>)</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Operations.html#Set.preimage\">⁻¹'</a> <span class=\"fn\">s</span>)</span>)</span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#setOf\">}</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#tangentConeAt_def","kind":"theorem","line":47,"name":"tangentConeAt_def","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.lean#L47-L66"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#tangentConeAt\"><span class=\"name\">tangentConeAt</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">R</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">E</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#AddCommGroup\">AddCommGroup</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#SMul\">SMul</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Basic.html#TopologicalSpace\">TopologicalSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set\">Set</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">E</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set\">Set</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The set of all tangent directions to the set `s` at the point `x`.\n\nA point `y` belongs to the tangent cone of `s` at `x` iff\nthere exist a family of scalars `c n`, a family of vectors `d n`,\nand a nontrivial filter in the index type such that\n\n- `d n → 0` along the filter;\n- `x + d n ∈ s` eventually along the filter;\n- `c n • d n → y` along the filter,\n\nThe actual definition is given in terms of cluster points of a filter,\nsee `mem_tangentConeAt_of_seq` and `exists_fun_of_mem_tangentConeAt`\nfor the two implications unfolding this definition in more convenient way.\n\nIn a space with first countable topology,\none can assume that the index type is `ℕ` and the filter is `atTop`,\nbut the definition we use is more useful without that assumption.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.html#tangentConeAt","kind":"def","line":47,"name":"tangentConeAt","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/TangentCone/Defs.lean#L47-L66"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.Analysis.Normed.Field.Basic","Mathlib.Order.Filter.Pointwise"],"instances":[],"name":"Mathlib.Analysis.Calculus.TangentCone.Defs"}